Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:47.41,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈願與你並肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:49.52,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:54.22,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正確與否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:56.57,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取決於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:04.44,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:11.35,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而詞不達意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.41,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}這也無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.87,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}讓弱小的我變得強大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:22.42,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是為與你相稱
Comment: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:26.90,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:28.90,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我難以割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:33.39,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}亦如無法放棄
